page.title: 20CONCLUSION & CREDITS
page.content: As you can see from our work,the area many of us live in is rural. There is only one shop in the whole D block, and one B road- the B1063, which passes from Cambridgeshire into Suffolk near Cropley Grove. The only river is nothing more than a stream passing through farming country. --------- PAGE 1&20:THE CLASS OF 7-9YR OLDS.
